description: This file contains test functions for a team-based agent system that provides information about national parks, utilizing models from external modules and defining a data model for park guides.

classes.name: ParkGuide
classes.description: A Pydantic data model representing a guide for a national park, including name, activities, and best season to visit.

methods.name: test_team_with_parser_model
methods.description: Test function that runs the team with a query about Yosemite National Park and asserts the response content.

methods.name: test_team_with_parser_model_stream
methods.description: Test function that runs the team in streaming mode and asserts the response content.
